data.description: Your own private oasis in a desirable Clairemont neighborhood!  Relax under the covered patio, and gaze out on your sparkling pool and palm trees. Stroll thru your bright and airy family room (no permit on family room), and into your upgraded kitchen with quartz counters, clean white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Ample skylights, three sets of french doors, and a cozy fireplace - all add to the charm.  Ownership is made easier with solar heated saltwater pool, owned photovoltaic solar, and efficient HVAC.  This home is ideally located - beyond the coastal fog line. The street/front yard has a clear view of Mount Soledad in La Jolla, so one can feel the cool breeze off the Pacific Ocean. It is a 3 minute walk to ample shopping at Clairemont Town Square, a 9 minute drive to La Jolla Shores, 10 minutes to UCSD, 16 minutes to downtown, and 19 minutes to San Diego International Airport.
